keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap d
map d removeTab
map a createTab
#map <m-[> previousTab
#map <m-]> nextTab
map h previousTab
map i nextTab
map n scrollPageDown
map k performFind
map K performBackwardsFind
map e scrollPageUp
map I goForward
map H goBack

g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
i: https://inside.corp.adobe.com/search.html#t=intranet&q=%s Inside Adobe
